      <title>大选临近，商业地产行业担心税收上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/commercial-real-estate-industry-worries-over-higher-taxes-election-looms-2024-10-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国商业房地产行业正努力争取前共和党总统唐纳德·特朗普倡导的税收减免和激励措施在下一届政府继续实施，因为该行业正努力应对不断飙升的拖欠率、创纪录的空置率以及融资成本上升的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/commercial-real-estate-industry-worries-over-higher-taxes-election-looms-2024-10-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
